metadata.name: CHINA DOLLS
metadata.description:
CHINA DOLLS
An original artwork by AprilYFU
5120 x 8192

China Doll where are you?
Where did you go?
Come back
My beautiful China Doll

Your heart may be broken
Shattered into pieces
But you have all the memories
Of the love that we shared

China Doll
You are missed
Your porcelain skin 
Lips so sweet

You have grace
So fair and beautiful
Little China Doll
Donâ€™t run away

There is a place for you
On the shelf, In my heart
I adore you 
And always will.

Poem by Angel.
